<h2>hvv switch</h2>

<h3>Description</h3>

<p>hvv switch integrates different mobility providers with in one App. The idea is to have access to all kind of mobility
in the greater Area of Hamburg with one App.</p>

<h3>MOSIAC part in Project</h3>

<p>MOSAIC did the integration of the different mobility provider, as well as the whole public transport ticketing process.
The whole business process of HVV switch is implemented by MOSAIC, so the most of the business objects are used by the
hvv switch App.</p>

<h3>Next Steps</h3>

<ul>
<li>Integrate a couple more mobility provider</li>
<li>Add some more features, e.g. Coupons
</br>
</br></li>
</ul>

<h2>hvv Any</h2>

<h3>Description</h3>

<p>An easy way to get your ticket with one click. The systems tracks your movement and afterwards you get calculate the best fare for your trip.</p>

<h3>MOSIAC part in Project</h3>

<p>Integrate the "Check-in / Be-out core system" from Scheidt &amp; Bachmann for trip calculation, best pricing and beacon management. Add services
to provide data for the "Check-in / Be-out core system", e.g. data for all Circulation, tariff information, collect all
sensor data from the smartphones as base for trip calculation. It was possible to focus in the project on the part
where expert knowledge is needed, create a algorithm for calculating trips and do best pricing.</p>

<h3>Next Steps</h3>

<ul>
<li>Best pricing up to one month.
</br>
</br></li>
</ul>

<h2>Self-Service-Terminal</h2>

<h3>Description</h3>

<p>This is the new version of our fare collection machine. It looks a bit like a big iPhone.</p>

<h3>MOSIAC part in Project</h3>

<p>The use the tariff-server from MOSAIC to get all Tariff details. In another step they will access the trip information system via MOSAIC.</p>

<h3>Next Steps</h3>

<ul>
<li>Integrate GTI Proxy</li>
<li>Integrate booking components via MOSAIC</li>
</ul>

<h2>VDV-Barcode</h2>

<h3>Description</h3>

<p>Generate all QR-Codes within the HVV.</p>

<h3>MOSIAC part in Project</h3>

<p>Integrate the SAM Server from ATOS Worldline to provide an easy to use interface to generate VDV Barcode. On one hand it is
possibile to generate just the barcode, with different level of information. On the other hand a barcode within a
printable layout can be generated.
